  "body": {
    "export_view": {
      "value": "<p>Released\u00a06/20/2017 11:45 AM CT (16:45 UTC)</p><h2 id=\"id-1.12.12-Repair/TradeinDiagnosticNotesFormatting\">Repair/Tradein Diagnostic Notes Formatting</h2><p>Backed by popular demand, when copy &amp; pasting information into the problem/diagnostics area\u00a0formatting\u00a0is now stripped and only content (text) is pasted in.\u00a0</p><h2 id=\"id-1.12.12-IntegratedPrintingOptimization\">Integrated Printing Optimization</h2><p>We have optimized Integrated Printing for windows.\u00a0If you run RepairQ with integrated\u00a0printing on a lower memory windows machine, you may have experienced slow print times, or crashes during the print process. This update should dramatically alleviate\u00a0these problems for low memory windows machines.</p><h2 id=\"id-1.12.12-SearchImprovements\">Search Improvements</h2><p>The search ranking algorithm has been improved for inventory,\u00a0repair devices, and catalog</p>",
